er way of sampling the diffuse information from Environment Lights"]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Importance Sampled Ambient"], "role": "item", "extent": [2812, 2844], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [2961, 3040], "text": ["Number of Samples of the Environment Light during diffuse calculations"]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Number of Diffuse Samples"], "role": "item", "extent": [2930, 2961], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [3076, 3154], "text": ["Realtime blurring of the cubemap based on the roughness of the object"]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Importance Sampled Reflections"], "role": "item", "extent": [3040, 3076], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [3186, 3266], "text": ["Number of Samples of the Environment Light during specular calculations"]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Number of Specular Samples"], "role": "item", "extent": [3154, 3186], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [3297, 3373], "text": ["Reverses the backsides to ensure they are shaded like the front"]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Shade Both Sides As Front"], "role": "item", "extent": [3266, 3297], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "parameters_item_group"}], "indent": 4, "level": 2, "text": ["Advanced"], "extent": [2793, 2812], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": null}], "indent": 0, "level": 1, "text": "Parameters", "role": "section", "extent": [417, 429], "container": true, "type": "parameters_section", "id": "parameters"}], "summary": [" Physically Based Viewport Shader "], "type": "root", "attrs": {"version": null, "tags": "sidefxlabs,  model, gamedev", "namespace": "labs", "internal": "labs::labs_shader", "context": "sop", "type": "node", "icon": "VOP/pbrmetallic"}, "title": ["Labs PBR Shader"]}